title: Got S+ on level 5 Poppy but no mastery token?
body: Is the system broken? Is it disabled?

replies.body: Do you possibly have a link to that match on match history or a screenshot of the S+? I'm checking your recent matches, and the most recent S+ I see for Poppy right now was back in 2016.
Was your game in SR or a different game mode? It's only obtainable from SR.
